.Dd 2021-01-26
.Dt POWEROFF 8
.Os init #VERSION#
.Sh NAME
.Nm poweroff
.Nd power-off the system
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
is a wrapper script to send
.Dq USR1
signal to
.Xr init 8
and initiate the shutdown sequence by executing
.Dq /etc/rc.d/shutdown poweroff .
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr reboot 8 ,
.Xr init 8 ,
.Xr halt 8 .
